WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:23.000
Nikola Tesla:
The Industrial Revolution…our greatest opus.

00:00:27.000 --> 00:00:29.000
Nikola Tesla:
An age of limitless progress

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:34.000
Galahad:
Sentinel Five, requesting an
immediate sonar payload drop.

00:00:34.000 --> 00:00:38.000
Airship Commander:
Galton deployment in three, two…

00:00:39.000 --> 00:00:47.000
Nikola Tesla:
I, Nikola Tesla am but a mere instrument in this time.
I find myself in strange company…

00:00:47.000 --> 00:00:48.000
Galahad:
You never cease to amaze, Nikola.

00:00:49.000 --> 00:00:53.000
Nikola Tesla:
A man of science amongst ancient
warriors and legends

00:00:56.000 --> 00:00:57.000
Isabeau:
Galahad, did you…?

00:00:57.000 --> 00:00:58.000
Galahad:
I saw it.

00:00:58.000 --> 00:00:59.000
Lafayette:
Saw what?

00:00:59.000 --> 00:01:00.000
Galahad:
Half-­‐Breeds.

00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:01.000
Isabeau:
Exactly.

00:01:02.000 --> 00:01:07.000
Nikola Tesla:
I serve an Order of Knights, who answer
not to our laws, but to history itself.

00:01:16.000 --> 00:01:21.000
Nikola Tesla:
My work gives them hope that we will
one day prevail against our enemies.

00:01:31.000 --> 00:01:38.000
Nikola Tesla:
But I fear, the very weapons I have created,
may one day be our downfall.

